assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Profarma Distribuidora de Produtos Farmacêuticos S.A., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the distribution and retail sale of pharmaceutical and hospital products in Brazil. The company operates through Distribution, and Retail segments. It also provides medicines, human drugs, personal hygiene, veterinary, perfumery, and cosmetic products. In addition, the company engages in the hospital, vaccines, and dermatological businesses. Further, it operates 214 retail stores under the Drogasmil, Farmalife, Tamoio, and Rede Rosário brands. Profarma Distribuidora de Produtos Farmacêuticos S.A. was incorporated in 1961 and is headquartered in Rio de Janeiro, Brazil.
